  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Blue Planet Fund</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Blue Planet Fund aims to protect and restore critical marine habitats that support coastal adaptation and climate mitigation (e.g. mangroves, seagrass, coral reefs), enhance small scale fisheries management capacities and market linkages, and support more sustainable aquaculture production. Overall the programme will help deliver greater protection for coastal populations to climate change through nature based solutions, and improve coastal populations&apos; livelihoods and prosperity through more effective and environmentally positive marine resource management. The programme is part of the Blue Planet Fund portfolio delivered by FCDO and Defra, and will be coordinated with other HMG Blue Planet Fund programmes and investments.</narrative>
  </description>
